CHARLES KHUZWAYO ISILO Samabandla Wonke, uZwelithini kaBhekuzulu, siyalulama esibhedlela lapho selashwa khona. Lezi zindaba zidalulwe nguNdunankulu waso, uMntwana uMangosuthu Buthelezi, izolo. "Ngiyathokoza ukuthi iNdlunkulu yaKwaLinduzulu, uMaNdlovu nami sichazelwe ngudokotela oyinhloko yethimba lodokotela abelapha iSilo ukuthi imizamo yabo ekwelapheni iSilo isahamba kahle, ngendlela ebenelisayo. Wathi emuva kokucwaninga kwabo ngempilo yeSilo, bayenela ukuthi imizamo yabo yokwelapha iSilo isahamba kahle." ISilo saphuthunyiswa esibhedlela esiseqophelweni eliphezulu futhi saze sangeniswa nasegunjini labasesimweni esibucayi ngenyanga eyedlule, emuva kokuxinwa yisifo sikashukela. Esitatimendeni esithunyelelwe imithombo yezindaba uMntwana waKwaPhindangene, uveze ukuthi  noNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo kuzwelonke uDkt Zweli Mkhize, uke wayozenelisa ngokuqhubekayo ngokwelashwa kweNgonyama. "Waze wangena yena luqobo egunjini lapho iSilo selashwa khona.  UNdlunkulu uMaNdlovu uke wangena egunjini eyozibonela ngamehlo akhe isimo sokwelashwa kweSilo. UNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo usiqinisekisile sobabili ukuthi imizamo yokwelapha iSilo isahamba ngendlela emenelisayo." UMntwana ube esegcizelela ukuthi kusazothatha isikhathi ngaphambi kokuba iSilo siphume nxa odokotela sebenele ukuthi sebenze konke ukuba silulame.